Package cl.clcert.rp

Class CompositeType

  • java.lang.Object
    • cl.clcert.rp.CompositeType
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TypeC, TypeD

    public class CompositeType
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that deals with the generation of random lists with weighed probability depending on an array with them. It receives the priority intervals already normalised, ie: 1, 2, 3 would be the possible values for the array if there is 3 intervals.
    Author:
    constanzacsori
